{"tha-ap410:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap410:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap410:0.3":"Todeyyattheraapadana ","tha-ap410:1.1":"“Rajasi vijayo nama, ","tha-ap410:1.2":"ketumatipuruttame; ","tha-ap410:1.3":"Suro vikkamasampanno, ","tha-ap410:1.4":"puramajjhavasi tada. ","tha-ap410:2.1":"Tassa ranno pamattassa, ","tha-ap410:2.2":"ataviyo samutthahum; ","tha-ap410:2.3":"Otara tundika ceva, ","tha-ap410:2.4":"rattham viddhamsayum tada. ","tha-ap410:3.1":"Paccante kupite khippam, ","tha-ap410:3.2":"sannipatesirindamo; ","tha-ap410:3.3":"Bhate ceva balatthe ca, ","tha-ap410:3.4":"arim niggahayi tada. ","tha-ap410:4.1":"Hattharoha anikattha, ","tha-ap410:4.2":"sura ca cammayodhino; ","tha-ap410:4.3":"Dhanuggaha ca ugga ca, ","tha-ap410:4.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:5.1":"Alarika ca kappaka, ","tha-ap410:5.2":"nhapaka malakaraka; ","tha-ap410:5.3":"Sura vijitasangama, ","tha-ap410:5.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:6.1":"Khaggahattha ca purisa, ","tha-ap410:6.2":"capahattha ca vammino; ","tha-ap410:6.3":"Ludda vijitasangama, ","tha-ap410:6.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:7.1":"Tidhapabhinna matanga, ","tha-ap410:7.2":"kunjara satthihayana; ","tha-ap410:7.3":"Suvannakacchalankara, ","tha-ap410:7.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:8.1":"Khama sitassa unhassa, ","tha-ap410:8.2":"ukkaruharanassa ca; ","tha-ap410:8.3":"Yodhajiva katakamma, ","tha-ap410:8.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:9.1":"Sankhasaddam bherisaddam, ","tha-ap410:9.2":"atho utujasaddakam; ","tha-ap410:9.3":"Etehi te hasayanta, ","tha-ap410:9.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:10.1":"Tisulakontimantehi ca, ","tha-ap410:10.2":"kavacatomarehi ca; ","tha-ap410:10.3":"Kottentanam nipatenta, ","tha-ap410:10.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap410:11.1":"Kimevatinisametva, ","tha-ap410:11.2":"saraja ajitam jino; ","tha-ap410:11.3":"Satthi panasahassani, ","tha-ap410:11.4":"sule uttasayim tada. ","tha-ap410:12.1":"Saddam manusakakamsu, ","tha-ap410:12.2":"‘aho raja adhammiko; ","tha-ap410:12.3":"Niraye paccamanassa, ","tha-ap410:12.4":"kada anto bhavissati’. ","tha-ap410:13.1":"Sayaneham tuvattento, ","tha-ap410:13.2":"passami niraye tada; ","tha-ap410:13.3":"Na supami divarattim, ","tha-ap410:13.4":"sulena tajjayanti mam. ","tha-ap410:14.1":"Kim pamadena rajjena, ","tha-ap410:14.2":"vahanena balena ca; ","tha-ap410:14.3":"Na te pahonti dharetum, ","tha-ap410:14.4":"tapayanti mamam sada. ","tha-ap410:15.1":"Kim me puttehi darehi, ","tha-ap410:15.2":"rajjena sakalena ca; ","tha-ap410:15.3":"Yannuna pabbajeyyaham, ","tha-ap410:15.4":"gatimaggam visodhaye. ","tha-ap410:16.1":"Satthi nagasahassani, ","tha-ap410:16.2":"sabbalankarabhusite; ","tha-ap410:16.3":"Suvannakacche matange, ","tha-ap410:16.4":"hemakappanavasase. ","tha-ap410:17.1":"Arulhe gamaniyehi, ","tha-ap410:17.2":"tomarankusapanibhi; ","tha-ap410:17.3":"Sangamavacare thane, ","tha-ap410:17.4":"anapekkho vihayaham; ","tha-ap410:17.5":"Sakakammena santatto, ","tha-ap410:17.6":"nikkhamim anagariyam. ","tha-ap410:18.1":"Satthi assasahassani, ","tha-ap410:18.2":"sabbalankarabhusite; ","tha-ap410:18.3":"Ajaniyeva jatiya, ","tha-ap410:18.4":"sindhave sighavahane. ","tha-ap410:19.1":"Arulhe gamaniyehi, ","tha-ap410:19.2":"capahatthehi vammibhi; ","tha-ap410:19.3":"Paharetvana te sabbe, ","tha-ap410:19.4":"nikkhamim anagariyam. ","tha-ap410:20.1":"Satthi rathasahassani, ","tha-ap410:20.2":"sabbalankarabhusite; ","tha-ap410:20.3":"Dipe athopi veyagghe, ","tha-ap410:20.4":"sannaddhe ussitaddhaje; ","tha-ap410:20.5":"Te sabbe pariharetva, ","tha-ap410:20.6":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap410:21.1":"Satthi dhenusahassani, ","tha-ap410:21.2":"sabba kamsupadharana; ","tha-ap410:21.3":"Tayopi chaddayitvana, ","tha-ap410:21.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap410:22.1":"Satthi itthisahassani, ","tha-ap410:22.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap410:22.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap410:22.4":"amukkamanikundala. ","tha-ap410:23.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap410:23.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap410:23.3":"Ta hitva kandamanayo, ","tha-ap410:23.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap410:24.1":"Satthi gamasahassani, ","tha-ap410:24.2":"paripunnani sabbaso; ","tha-ap410:24.3":"Chaddayitvana tam rajjam, ","tha-ap410:24.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap410:25.1":"Nagara nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap410:25.2":"himavantamupagamim; ","tha-ap410:25.3":"Bhagirathinaditire, ","tha-ap410:25.4":"assamam mapayim aham. ","tha-ap410:26.1":"Pannasalam karitvana, ","tha-ap410:26.2":"Agyagaram akasaham; ","tha-ap410:26.3":"Araddhaviriyo pahitatto, ","tha-ap410:26.4":"Vasami assame aham. ","tha-ap410:27.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","tha-ap410:27.2":"sunnagare ca jhayato; ","tha-ap410:27.3":"Na tu vijjati taso me, ","tha-ap410:27.4":"na passe bhayabheravam. ","tha-ap410:28.1":"Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap410:28.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap410:28.3":"Nanalokena jotanto, ","tha-ap410:28.4":"loke uppajji tavade. ","tha-ap410:29.1":"Mama assamasamanta, ","tha-ap410:29.2":"yakkho asi mahiddhiko; ","tha-ap410:29.3":"Buddhasetthamhi uppanne, ","tha-ap410:29.4":"arocesi mamam tada. ","tha-ap410:30.1":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap410:30.2":"sumedho nama cakkhuma; ","tha-ap410:30.3":"Tareti janatam sabbam, ","tha-ap410:30.4":"tampi so tarayissati’. ","tha-ap410:31.1":"Yakkhassa vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap410:31.2":"samviggo asi tavade; ","tha-ap410:31.3":"Buddho buddhoti cintento, ","tha-ap410:31.4":"assamam patisamayim. ","tha-ap410:32.1":"Aggidarunca chaddetva, ","tha-ap410:32.2":"samsametvana santhatam; ","tha-ap410:32.3":"Assamam abhivanditva, ","tha-ap410:32.4":"nikkhamim vipina aham. ","tha-ap410:33.1":"Tato candanamadaya, ","tha-ap410:33.2":"gama gamam pura puram; ","tha-ap410:33.3":"Devadevam gavesanto, ","tha-ap410:33.4":"upagacchim vinayakam. ","tha-ap410:34.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap410:34.2":"sumedho lokanayako; ","tha-ap410:34.3":"Catusaccam pakasento, ","tha-ap410:34.4":"bodheti janatam bahum. ","tha-ap410:35.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap410:35.2":"sise katvana candanam; ","tha-ap410:35.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap410:35.4":"ima gatha abhasaham. ","tha-ap410:36.1":"‘Vassike pupphamanamhi, ","tha-ap410:36.2":"santike upavayati; ","tha-ap410:36.3":"Tvam vira gunagandhena, ","tha-ap410:36.4":"disa sabba pavayasi. ","tha-ap410:37.1":"Campake nagavanike, ","tha-ap410:37.2":"atimuttakaketake; ","tha-ap410:37.3":"Salesu pupphamanesu, ","tha-ap410:37.4":"anuvatam pavayati. ","tha-ap410:38.1":"Tava gandham sunitvana, ","tha-ap410:38.2":"himavanta idhagamim; ","tha-ap410:38.3":"Pujemi tam mahavira, ","tha-ap410:38.4":"lokajettha mahayasa’. ","tha-ap410:39.1":"Varacandanenanulimpim, ","tha-ap410:39.2":"sumedham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap410:39.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap410:39.4":"tunhi atthasi tavade. ","tha-ap410:40.1":"Sumedho nama bhagava, ","tha-ap410:40.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap410:40.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap410:40.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap410:41.1":"‘Yo me gune pakittesi, ","tha-ap410:41.2":"candananca apujayi; ","tha-ap410:41.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap410:41.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap410:42.1":"Adeyyavakyavacano, ","tha-ap410:42.2":"brahma uju patapava; ","tha-ap410:42.3":"Pancavisatikappani, ","tha-ap410:42.4":"sappabhaso bhavissati. ","tha-ap410:43.1":"Chabbisatikappasate, ","tha-ap410:43.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap410:43.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap410:43.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap410:44.1":"Tettimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap410:44.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap410:44.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap410:44.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap410:45.1":"Tato cutoyam manujo, ","tha-ap410:45.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap410:45.3":"Punnakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap410:45.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap410:46.1":"Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap410:46.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap410:46.3":"Tilakkhanena sampanno, ","tha-ap410:46.4":"bavari nama brahmano. ","tha-ap410:47.1":"Tassa sisso bhavitvana, ","tha-ap410:47.2":"hessati mantaparagu; ","tha-ap410:47.3":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap410:47.4":"gotamam sakyapungavam. ","tha-ap410:48.1":"Pucchitva nipune panhe, ","tha-ap410:48.2":"bhavayitvana anjasam; ","tha-ap410:48.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap410:48.4":"viharissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap410:49.1":"Tividhaggi nibbuta mayham, ","tha-ap410:49.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap410:49.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap410:49.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap410:50.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap410:50.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap410:50.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap410:51.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap410:51.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap410:51.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap410:52.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap410:52.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap410:52.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap410:53.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma todeyyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap410:54.1":"Todeyyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}